high_descs: Turn around, then to the left to find the fridge.
Take out a bowl from the fridge.
Carry the bowl and turn to the left, then find the sink on the right.
Place the bowl inside the sink, and turn on the water. Turn it off and pick up the bowl.
Hold the bowl and turn to the right and go back to the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the bowl inside, then shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Rinse a bowl and place it in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around, step forward, then turn left to approach the fridge.
Take the bowl from the freezer.
Go to the sink behind you, to the left of the coffee maker.
Clean the bowl and fill it with water in the sink.
Turn around and go back to the fridge.
Put the bowl in the freezer.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean bowl with water in it in the freezer.

high_descs: Go to the refrigerator on your right.
Remove the frosted bowl, on the top shelf of the freezer.
Turn around and go to the sink.
Place the bowl in the sink, turn the water on, fill the bowl with water, turn the water off, and remove the bowl from the sink.
Turn to your right and go to the refrigerator.
Place the bowl of water, in the freezer, on the bottom shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold bowl of water in the freezer.
